OL,3,CAngela Rayner says she has been
OL,4,Ccleared by HMRC after stamp duty row
OL,6,FAngela Rayner tells ITV News UK Editor
OL,7,FPaul Brand that she was "horrified" at
OL,8,Fthe idea she had not paid the correct
OL,9,Ftax and "welcomed" HMRC clearing her
OL,10,Fof any wrongdoing after a probe into
OL,11,Funderpaid stamp duty.
OL,13,FAngela Rayner says she has been
OL,14,Fcleared of tax avoidance by HMRC and
OL,15,Fwill not face a fine or penalty after
OL,16,Fa row over underpaid stamp duty last
OL,17,Fyear forced her to resign from
OL,18,Fgovernment.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
