OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1778760671
OL,3,CAngela Rayner says she has been
OL,4,Ccleared by HMRC after stamp duty row
OL,6,FThe Labour MP stepped down as deputy
OL,7,Fprime minister and housing secretary
OL,8,Flast September when an independent
OL,9,Fethics advisor found she had broken
OL,10,Fministerial code after admitting she
OL,11,Fhad underpaid stamp duty on an
OL,12,F#800,000 flat in Hove, which was
OL,13,Fconsidered to be her second home.
OL,15,FOn Thursday, Rayner announced an HMRC
OL,16,Finvestigation had cleared her of any
OL,17,Fwrongdoing after concluding Rayner had
OL,18,Fnot sought to avoid paying the correct
OL,19,Fstamp duty on the purchase of her
OL,20,Fproperty in 2025.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
