PN,30703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1778760671
OL,3,CAngela Rayner says she has been
OL,4,Ccleared by HMRC after stamp duty row
OL,6,FIn a statement, she said, while HMRC's
OL,7,Finvestigation found stamp duty was
OL,8,Fpayable at the higher rate, the probe
OL,9,Fconcluded she acted with reasonable
OL,10,Fcare and was not at fault and has paid
OL,11,Fthe stamp duty due on the property at
OL,12,Fthe higher rate.
OL,14,FThe MP for Ashton-under-Lyne said she
OL,15,Fwelcomed HMRC's conclusion.
OL,17,F"I have been exonerated by HMRC of the
OL,18,Faccusation I deliberately sought to
OL,19,Favoid tax," she said.
OL,26,@yD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
