PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1778760671
OL,3,CAngela Rayner says she has been
OL,4,Ccleared by HMRC after stamp duty row
OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV News' UK Editor Paul
OL,7,FBrand, Rayner said she had "accepted
OL,8,FHMRC's finding".
OL,10,F"They've said that there wasn't any
OL,11,Fwrongdoing and that I didn't try to
OL,12,Favoid paying tax or I wasn't careless
OL,13,Fin the way in which I conducted myself
OL,14,Fat the time when I was in government."
OL,16,FShe continued: "I'd taken advice and
OL,17,Ffelt I'd done the right thing and it
OL,18,Fwas right for me to stand down from
OL,19,Fgovernment and to comply with HMRC,
OL,20,Fwhich is what I've done."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1778760671
OL,3,CAngela Rayner says she has been
OL,4,Ccleared by HMRC after stamp duty row
OL,6,FRayner faced mounting pressure over
OL,7,Fher political future last autumn over
OL,8,Fthe underpaid stamp duty. She
OL,9,Finitially said she had been advised
OL,10,Fshe was not liable for the second
OL,11,Fproperty surcharge because she had
OL,12,Fsold her stake in her family home in
OL,13,FAshton-under-Lyne to a trust
OL,14,Festablished in 2020 to benefit her
OL,15,Fdisabled son.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
