PN,30706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1778760671
OL,3,CAngela Rayner says she has been
OL,4,Ccleared by HMRC after stamp duty row
OL,6,FRayner told ITV News: "I've never
OL,7,Fwanted to avoid paying my tax. For me,
OL,8,Fthat was the most distressing thing,
OL,9,Fthat people felt that I was tax
OL,10,Fdodging or trying to set up trusts to
OL,11,Favoid tax, or being careless by not
OL,12,Ftaking the appropriate advice. And
OL,13,FHMRC has concluded that that isn't the
OL,14,Fcase."
OL,16,FShe said she had been "hurt" by the
OL,17,Fcoverage surrounding her tax affairs.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
