CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1778760671
OL,3,CAngela Rayner says she has been
OL,4,Ccleared by HMRC after stamp duty row
OL,6,F"I didn't want people to think that
OL,7,Fthe person they know me as, the person
OL,8,Fwho went into politics to fight for
OL,9,Fpeople, suddenly dropped all their
OL,10,Fvalues and was just on the take. And
OL,11,Fthat's never been me. And I was
OL,12,Fhorrified that that's what the
OL,13,Fconsequences could have been, that I'd
OL,14,Fdone something wrong," she said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
