OL,3,CAngela Rayner says she has been
OL,4,Ccleared by HMRC after stamp duty row
OL,6,FAt the time, she conceded she had made
OL,7,Fa "mistake" after fresh legal advice
OL,8,Ffrom a "leading tax counsel" later
OL,9,Frevealed that she was liable. Rayner
OL,10,Ftold ITV News that her lawyers have
OL,11,Ftold her this is a particularly
OL,12,Fcomplex, niche and ambiguous area of
OL,13,Ftax.
