OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1778760671
OL,3,CAngela Rayner says she has been
OL,4,Ccleared by HMRC after stamp duty row
OL,6,FIn a statement at the time, Rayner
OL,7,Fadmitted: "I acknowledge that due to
OL,8,Fmy reliance on advice from lawyers
OL,9,Fwhich did not properly take account of
OL,10,Fthese provisions, I did not pay the
OL,11,Fappropriate stamp duty at the time of
OL,12,Fthe purchase."
OL,14,FThe announcement comes at a critical
OL,15,Ftime for the Labour Party as Keir
OL,16,FStarmer fights for his premiership
OL,17,Ffollowing a revolt by Labour MPs after
OL,18,Flast week's disastrous election
OL,19,Fresults.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
