OL,3,CAngela Rayner says she has been
OL,4,Ccleared by HMRC after stamp duty row
OL,6,FEarlier this week, Rayner called on
OL,7,FStarmer to "set out the change our
OL,8,Fcountry needs" as she warned Labour is
OL,9,Ffacing its "last chance" after a
OL,10,Fdisastrous set of election results.
OL,12,FRayner, who has long been seen as a
OL,13,Fpotential successor to the prime
OL,14,Fminister, stopped short of calling for
OL,15,Fhim to quit, but set out a series of
OL,16,Fsteps he needed to take to win back
OL,17,Fworking-class voters.
OL,26,@oD@LOUpD@NO]qD@LOUqD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
