OL,3,CAngela Rayner says she has been
OL,4,Ccleared by HMRC after stamp duty row
OL,6,FShe added that it had been a mistake
OL,7,Fto block Andy Burnham's possible
OL,8,Freturn to Westminster, saying Labour
OL,9,Fneeds to bring its "best players into
OL,10,FParliament".
OL,12,FBurnham is also seen as a potential
OL,13,Frival to Starmer, and the potential
OL,14,Fsoft-left choice, but his attempt to
OL,15,Fstand in the Gorton and Denton by-
OL,16,Felection was thwarted by Labour's
OL,17,Fhierarchy.
OL,26,@qD@TOUrD@KO]
